{"tid":1920430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【藍店】許留山遭入稟申請清盤","createTime":"2020-03-11T12:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T18:09:32.000Z","uid":202464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90d6e4ebcbe92d73bdf2b378727b8867a87f5e0c","tid":1920430,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"被多名業主追討舖租的甜品品牌「許留山」，今日（11日）遭權記玩具有限公司入稟高等法院申請清盤。<br />\n<br />\n許留山過去數月已關閉10餘間門店，主要集中在旅遊區和個別住宅區，形容公司業務去年受反修例運動巨大衝擊，來港遊客急劇減少，導致其傳統旅遊區門店業務減少六至七成。<br />\n<br />\n許留山位於藍田匯景廣場的分店再遭業主Bansque Limited入稟高等法院，要求收回舖位，以及追討分店去年10月開始拖欠、逾19萬元的租金。"},{"pid":"f2bfdb0ff6e49b465528cd5381363e8288ca55e5","tid":1920430,"uid":309935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"f47e99523a97139a2f13ed99a911d3a5fd7f2415","tid":1920430,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"如果當日開溫書區就唔使咁既下場啦"},{"pid":"6e7d156f0cf042e87d8c833f407fda4c42f24bbd","tid":1920430,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0ff2b073450d23ab88e2abf2f91833c3f6f6b8","tid":1920430,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"本來芒椰舔閪有資格成為香港特色飲品<br />\n但藍既就死都唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50acda838fc454f124c723518779b427e10c835","tid":1920430,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8fb5e116051218de785ea9fa56f88cf4220d08","tid":